668
01:17:27,719 --> 01:17:30,221
Chẳng phải vậy sao?

669
01:17:30,304 --> 01:17:32,306
Đúng, trừ phi...

670
01:17:34,058 --> 01:17:36,060
Trừ phi?

671
01:17:37,645 --> 01:17:39,939
